Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.37,0:22:45.39,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}一定要给你树旗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.65,0:22:48.24,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an1}{\fad(100,100)}你是看不到的
